<%- layout(`Boilerplate/boilerplate`) %>

<link
  rel="stylesheet"
  href="/Stylesheets/SEO ANALYSIS/seo-analysis-styles.css"
/>

<%- include('../../Solutions-Card/solutionsCard.ejs') %>

<div class="seo-analysis-container">
  <div class="seo-analysis-form-container">
    <div class="seo-analysis-prompt">
      <h1 class="bold-text text-white">
        COMPREHENSIVE SEO ANALYSIS FOR <br />
        <span>STARTUPS, SMBS, AND ENTERPRISES</span>
      </h1>
      <h5 class="bold-text text-white">
        WHAT'S YOUR WEBSITE'S OPTIMIZATION SCORE?
      </h5>
    </div>

    <div class="feedback">
      <div id="spinner-overlay" style="z-index: 9999">
        <div
          class="spinner-border spinner text-white spinner-border-sm"
          role="status"
          style="display: none"
        ></div>
      </div>

      <span style="display: none" id="msg-span" class="text-white"
        >Thank you for submitting your information, you'll receive your FREE SEO
        ANALYSIS in the next 12 to 24hr.</span
      >
    </div>

    <form class="seo-analysis-form d-g">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Your Full Name" required />
      <input type="email" placeholder="Enter Your Email Address" required />
      <input type="number" placeholder="Enter Phone Number" required />
      <div class="url-input d-g">
        <input type="url" placeholder="Enter Your Website URL" required />
        <button class="text-white">ANALYZE</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
  <div class="more-about-company">
    <h5 class="more-about-company-title bold-text text-title-size mb-5">
      IN-DEPTH SEO <br />
      <span class="more-about-company-title-span text-title-color"
        >WEBSITE AUDIT</span
      >
    </h5>

    <div class="more-about-business-btns bg-white d-f mb-5">
      <button class="business-btn d-flex">WEBSITE CRAWLING</button>
      <button class="business-btn d-flex">INDEXATION ISSUES</button>
      <button class="business-btn d-flex">FULL SITE DIRECTORY</button>
      <button class="business-btn d-flex">METADATA CHECK</button>
      <button class="business-btn d-flex">ANALYSING PERFORMANCE</button>
    </div>

    <div class="info-holder mt-3">
      <div class="container-of-info d-f" style="display: none" id="btn1">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/website_crawling.jpg"
          class="solutions-main-image"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="info">
          <div class="more-info mb-4">
            <label class="info-holder-label text-title-color bold-text mb-3"
              >WEBSITE CRAWLING</label
            >
            <p class="info-holder-text">
              If certain pages on your website cannot be accessed by search
              engines, there is a possibility that your site might not be
              properly indexed or may not be indexed at all. When your website
              doesn't appear in the index, it becomes inaccessible to users who
              are trying to find it. We thoroughly examine your website to
              identify any crawlability issues that hinder search engine bots
              from properly indexing your content. We analyse robots.txt files,
              XML sitemaps, and internal linking structures to ensure optimal
              crawlability and discoverability of your web pages.
            </p>
            <a href="/become-client" class="connect-btn bold-text">
              LETS CONNECT
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container-of-info d-f" style="display: none" id="btn2">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/indexation_issues.jpg"
          class="solutions-main-image"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="info">
          <div class="more-info mb-4">
            <label class="info-holder-label text-title-color bold-text mb-3"
              >INDEXATION ISSUES</label
            >
            <p class="info-holder-text">
              Achieving proper indexing of your pages is crucial for your
              visibility on Google search results. Indexation issues arise when
              search engines struggle to index and understand your website's
              pages accurately. Our audit process includes a meticulous review
              of your website's indexation status to identify potential issues.
              We examine canonical tags, duplicate content, and URL parameters
              to ensure that search engines can effectively index and display
              your web pages in search results. By resolving indexation issues,
              we help search engines better comprehend your content, leading to
              improved rankings and increased organic traffic.
            </p>
            <a href="/become-client" class="connect-btn bold-text">
              LETS CONNECT
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container-of-info d-f" style="display: none" id="btn3">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/sitemap.jpg"
          class="solutions-main-image"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="info">
          <div class="more-info mb-4">
            <label class="info-holder-label text-title-color bold-text mb-3"
              >FULL SITE DIRECTORY</label
            >
            <p class="info-holder-text">
              A Full Site Directory serves as a vital tool for search engines to
              understand your website's structure and content. An XML-based Full
              Site Directory facilitates Google in navigating through the
              essential pages on your website. During this stage, we carefully
              analyze your Full Site Directory to ensure it is properly
              structured, up-to-date, and includes all relevant pages. We verify
              that all URLs are correctly included and that the directory
              adheres to search engine guidelines. By optimizing your Full Site
              Directory, we enable search engines to crawl and index your
              website more efficiently, enhancing its visibility and
              discoverability
            </p>
            <a href="/become-client" class="connect-btn bold-text">
              LETS CONNECT
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container-of-info d-f" style="display: none" id="btn4">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/metadata_check.jpg"
          class="solutions-main-image"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="info">
          <div class="more-info mb-4">
            <label class="info-holder-label text-title-color bold-text mb-3"
              >METADATA CHECK</label
            >
            <p class="info-holder-text">
              While Google may not always display meta descriptions
              (approximately 37% of the time), it is still crucial to optimise
              them for your most important pages.In this phase, we review your
              website's metadata, such as title tags, meta descriptions, and
              header tags. We ensure that they are unique, relevant, and
              optimised with targeted keywords to improve search engine
              visibility and encourage higher click-through rates from search
              results. By optimising your metadata, we enhance your website's
              appearance in search listings, increasing the likelihood of
              attracting qualified traffic and improving your overall SEO
              performance.
            </p>
            <a href="/become-client" class="connect-btn bold-text">
              LETS CONNECT
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container-of-info d-f" style="display: none" id="btn5">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/analysing_performance.jpg"
          class="solutions-main-image"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="info">
          <div class="more-info mb-4">
            <label class="info-holder-label text-title-color bold-text mb-3"
              >ANALYSING PERFORMANCE</label
            >
            <p class="info-holder-text">
              Website performance impacts user experience and search engine
              rankings. In order to enhance user experience, Google strives to
              improve website speed, as slow-loading sites are generally
              disliked by users. During this stage of our SEO audit process, we
              assess your website's performance metrics, including page load
              speed, mobile responsiveness, and overall user experience. We
              identify any performance bottlenecks that may negatively impact
              user engagement and search engine rankings. Our recommendations
              aim to optimise your website's performance, ensuring faster
              loading times, seamless user experiences, and ultimately, higher
              search engine rankings and increased conversions.
            </p>
            <a href="/become-client" class="connect-btn bold-text">
              LETS CONNECT
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="game-changing-analysis-container">
    <div
      class="game-changing-analysis-header bold-text"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-delay="400"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
      data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
    >
      <h1 class="text-title-size mb-3">
        EXPERIENCE A GAME-CHANGING <br />
        <span class="text-title-color">SEO ANALYSIS</span>
      </h1>
      <p>
        Digital Benders believes in delivering exceptional SEO analysis services
        to help businesses thrive online.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="game-changing-analysis-main">
      <div
        class="game-changing-analysis m-l"
        data-aos="fade-right"
        data-aos-delay="400"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
      >
        <label class="text-title-color bold-text mt-1 mb-3">SEO RESULTS</label>
        <p>
          We delve into critical factors such as keyword optimization, on-page
          elements, and technical SEO to assess your website's visibility and
          effectiveness.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="game-changing-analysis m-r"
        data-aos="fade-left"
        data-aos-delay="400"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
      >
        <label class="text-title-color bold-text mt-1 mb-3"
          >TECHNICAL AUDIT</label
        >
        <p>
          We examine the technical health of your website, identifying issues
          like crawl errors, slow page speeds, broken links, and mobile
          usability problems that could affect search engine performance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="game-changing-analysis m-l"
        data-aos="fade-right"
        data-aos-delay="400"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
      >
        <label class="text-title-color bold-text mt-1 mb-3"
          >CONTENT QUALITY</label
        >
        <p>
          We evaluate the depth, originality, and relevance of your website
          content to ensure it aligns with user intent and supports strong
          ranking signals across search engines.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="game-changing-analysis m-r"
        data-aos="fade-left"
        data-aos-delay="400"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
      >
        <label class="text-title-color bold-text mt-1 mb-3"
          >BACKLINK PROFILE</label
        >
        <p>
          Our analysis reviews your backlink structure, identifying
          opportunities for high-authority links and detecting toxic backlinks
          that may harm your SEO credibility.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="game-changing-analysis m-l"
        data-aos="fade-right"
        data-aos-delay="400"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
      >
        <label class="text-title-color bold-text mt-1 mb-3"
          >USER EXPERIENCE</label
        >
        <p>
          We assess navigation, layout, and accessibility to ensure your website
          delivers an intuitive, engaging, and conversion-optimized experience
          for all users.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="/Javascripts/SEO ANALYSIS/seo-analysis-js/businessBtns.js"></script>

<script>
  const form = document.querySelector(`.seo-analysis-form`);
  const span = document.querySelector(`#msg-span`);
  const spinner = document.querySelector(`.spinner`);

  form.addEventListener(`submit`, (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    span.style.display = "none";

    if (spinner) {
      spinner.style.display = "inline-block";
      setTimeout(() => {
        spinner.style.display = "none";
        span.style.display = "block";
        form.reset();

        if (span.style.display === "block") {
          setTimeout(() => {
            span.style.display = "none";
          }, 5000);
        }
      }, 3000);
    }
  });
</script>
